<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>عَن حَكَمٍ لَهُ اعْتِبَارٌ في المَلاَ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>يَنْظُرُ في دَعْوَاهُمَا بِالدِّقَّة<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>عَسَاهُ يُعْطِي الحَقَّ مُسْتَحِقَّه<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>فَسَارَ لِلْبَحْثِ بِلاَ تَوَاني<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>مُفْتَخِرَاً بِثِقَةِ الإِخْوَانِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>يَقُولُ عِنْدِي فِكْرَةٌ مُثِيرَة<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>تَرْفَعُ شَأْنَ التَّيْسِ في الْعَشِيرَة<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَذَاكَ أَنَّ أَفْضَلَ الثَّنَاءِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>مَا جَاءَ عَلَى أَلْسُنِ الأَعْدَاءِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>لِذَا فَإِنيِّ إِنْ دَعَوْتُ الذِّيبَا<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>لاَ يَسْتَطِيعَانِ لَهُ تَكْذِيبَا<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>فَجَاءَ لِلذِّئْبِ وَقَالَ غَايَتي<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>أَنْتَ فَسِرْ مَعِي وَخُذْ بِلِحْيَتي<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>وَقَادَهُ لِلْمَوْضِعِ المَعْرُوفِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>فَقَامَ بَيْنَ الظَّبيَ وَالخَرُوفِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَقَالَ أَنَا لاَ أَقْضِي بِالظَّاهِرِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>فَمَزَّقَ الخَصْمَينِ بِالأَظَافِرِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَقَالَ لِلتَّيْسِ انْطَلِقْ لِشَأْنِكَا<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>مَا قَتَلَ الخَصْمَيْن غَيْرُ ذِقْنِكَا<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span><span class="c3">{أَمِيرُ الشُّعَرَاء / أَحْمَد شَوْقِي بِتَصَرُّف}</span><a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>